paper_abstract: In this paper, we discuss the boundedness and compactness of the product of extended Cesar operator and composition operator from the logarithmic Bloch-type space to F(p, q, s) space on the unit ball of C-n.
paper_title: PRODUCT OF EXTENDED CESARO OPERATOR AND COMPOSITION OPERATOR FROM THE LOGARITHMIC BLOCH-TYPE SPACE TO F(p, q, s) SPACE ON THE UNIT BALL
